  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200C.",
    "Toss pumpkin cubes with olive oil, minced garlic, cumin, coriander, turmeric, salt, and pepper.",
    "Spread pumpkin in a single layer on a baking sheet.",
    "Roast for 30 minutes, stirring halfway through.",
    "While roasting, combine water, torn lime leaves, lemon juice, and honey in a small pot.",
    "Bring the mixture to a gentle simmer and reduce for 5 minutes.",
    "Remove pumpkin from oven and drizzle the lime‑honey reduction over it.",
    "Return to oven and roast for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "Let the pumpkin rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with extra torn lime leaves if desired."
  ],
